> "Being where you want at the speed of thought."(^)


You can do anything in about three keystrokes!

vim is...
- ergonomic!
- efficient!
- intuitive!
-  powerful!

- ~100 year old (released 1991, to be more specific)
- well established, good code base (*)
- universal (text editor, browser, OS...)


